text: Gymnothorax longinquus is a moray eel found in coral reefs in the southwest Pacific Ocean.Gymnothorax longinquus at www.fishbase.org. It is commonly known as the yellow-gilled reef-eel, yellow-gilled moray, brown moray-eel, or long moray.Common names for Gymnothorax longinquus at www.fishbase.org. ==References== longinquus Category:Fish described in 1948
